This node module let you see console of other commands.
It is design that when you run a task in the background, you can see the task console, and send your command to it.

for example:

install by using:

	npm i -g node-remote-console

Use:

On the server:
	node-remote-console --listen port command

On the client:
	node-remote-console --connect ip port

for example:

	node-remote-console --listen 127.0.0.1 123
	node-remote-console --connect 127.0.0.1 123 cmd.exe



